valuesByMode.1406:2: Our San Francisco-grown watermelons are a juicy delight for your taste buds. Grown in the heart of the city, these watermelons are bursting with flavor and have a crisp texture that is unmatched. Each watermelon is carefully hand-picked at the peak of ripeness to ensure maximum flavor and freshness. Whether you enjoy them as a refreshing snack on a hot day, in a delicious watermelon salad, or as a centerpiece for your next summer gathering, these watermelons are sure to impress. With their vibrant color and mouthwatering taste, our San Francisco watermelons are a must-try for anyone who loves high-quality, locally sourced produce.
valuesByMode.1406:3: Our New York-grown cherries are a delicious treat for the senses. Grown in the heart of the city, these cherries are bursting with flavor and have a firm texture that is unmatched. Each cherry is carefully hand-picked at the peak of ripeness to ensure maximum flavor and freshness. Whether you enjoy them as a snack, in your favorite recipe, or as a beautiful addition to your next charcuterie board, these cherries are sure to impress. With their vibrant color and mouthwatering taste, our New York cherries are a must-try for anyone who loves high-quality, locally sourced produce.
valuesByMode.1406:4: Our New Jersey-grown pears are a delicious treat for your taste buds. Grown in the heart of the Garden State, these pears are bursting with flavor and have a crisp texture that is unmatched. Each pear is carefully hand-picked at the peak of ripeness to ensure maximum flavor and freshness. Whether you enjoy them as a healthy snack, in a decadent pear tart, or as a complement to your next cheese board, these pears are sure to impress. With their juicy sweetness and delicate aroma, our New Jersey pears are a must-try for anyone who loves high-quality, locally sourced produce.
valuesByMode.1406:5: Our Texas-grown shiitake mushrooms are a savory delight for your taste buds. Grown in the heart of the Lone Star State, these mushrooms are bursting with flavor and have a meaty texture that is unmatched. Each mushroom is carefully cultivated to ensure maximum flavor and freshness. Whether you enjoy them in a hearty stir-fry, as a meat substitute in your favorite recipe, or as a topping for your next pizza, these shiitake mushrooms are sure to impress. With their umami flavor and satisfying chewiness, our Texas shiitake mushrooms are a must-try for anyone who loves high-quality, locally sourced produce.
valuesByMode.1406:6: Our Ohio-grown kale is a nutritious delight for your taste buds. Grown in the heart of the Buckeye State, this kale is bursting with flavor and has a tender texture that is unmatched. Each leaf is carefully hand-picked to ensure maximum freshness and nutrient density. Whether you enjoy it in a delicious salad, as a side dish, or in your favorite smoothie, this kale is sure to impress. With its deep green color and earthy flavor, our Ohio kale is a must-try for anyone who loves high-quality, locally sourced produce. Plus, it's packed with vitamins and minerals to keep you healthy and energized.
valuesByMode.1406:7: Our Detroit-grown radishes are a crunchy and spicy delight for your taste buds. Grown in the heart of the Motor City, these radishes are bursting with flavor and have a crisp texture that is unmatched. Each radish is carefully harvested to ensure maximum freshness and flavor. Whether you enjoy them as a snack, sliced thinly in a salad, or pickled for a tangy kick, these radishes are sure to impress. With their vibrant color and bold taste, our Detroit radishes are a must-try for anyone who loves high-quality, locally sourced produce. Plus, they're packed with nutrients to support a healthy diet.
valuesByMode.1406:9: Farm Fresh Cremini Mushrooms are a delicious and versatile variety known for their earthy flavor and firm texture. These brown beauties, grown in pristine farm conditions, are perfect for adding depth to soups, stir-fries, and pasta dishes. Packed with nutrients, they're a healthy addition to any culinary creation.
